"To Kudo Shinichi"
It's to me.

156
00:10:06,266 --> 00:10:08,033
"Moriya Teiji"?

157
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,976
The Moriya Teiji?

158
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:15,609
"Please forgive the
suddenness of my letter."

159
00:10:15,633 --> 00:10:18,509
"I've heard much about your exploits
as a high school detective

160
00:10:18,533 --> 00:10:22,343
in the newspapers and on television,

161
00:10:22,367 --> 00:10:27,309
and very much wanted the chance
to speak with you in person."

162
