but the timer isn't stopping...

1261
01:23:26,226 --> 01:23:29,108
P-plus there are still two cords left!

1262
01:23:29,132 --> 01:23:30,608
A red one and a blue one!

1263
01:23:30,632 --> 01:23:31,865
What?!

1264
01:23:35,299 --> 01:23:39,132
The path to the 4th floor
stairway is finally open!

1265
01:23:39,426 --> 01:23:43,386
Hurry! There's only four
minutes until it detonates!

1266
01:23:43,411 --> 01:23:45,312
Ran! Ran!
I'm coming!

1267
01:23:45,466 --> 01:23:46,447
Mori-san!

1268
01:23:46,532 --> 01:23:48,541
Where are you going, Mori-san?!

1269
01:23:48,565 --> 01:23:51,875
Let go of me!
I have to save Ran!

1270
01:23:51,899 --> 01:23:54,442
Please stop!
The rescue team will save-

1271
01:23:54,466 --> 01:23:56,798
Ran! Ran!

1272
01:23:57,798 --> 01:24:00,865
The hapless love of a father
for his daughter...

1273
01:24:01,108 --> 01:24:03,342
Architecture has no need for love...

1274
01:24:03,366 --> 01:24:04,899
Nor does life!

1275
01:24:06,346 --> 01:24:10,346
Wait, Professor! Don't tell me
you purposely left out the two wires

1276
01:24:10,371 --> 01:24:12,191
to set me up?!

1277
01:24:12,879 --> 01:24:15,446
What should I do?
Cut them both?

1278
01:24:15,471 --> 01:24:17,981
You idiot!
One of them's a booby trap!

1279
01:24:18,029 --> 01:24:19,606
It'll blow the instant you cut it!

1280
01:24:19,631 --> 01:24:21,465
A-are you serious?!

1281
01:24:29,049 --> 01:24:31,242
Damn! Which is it?!

1282
01:24:31,266 --> 01:24:34,132
Red or blue?!
Which should we cut?!

1283
01:24:49,804 --> 01:24:52,797
Midnight...
Three minutes left...

1284
01:24:52,974 --> 01:24:55,974
Damn it! Which is it?!
Which one?!

1285
01:24:56,198 --> 01:24:57,072
Shinichi?

1286
01:24:57,705 --> 01:24:58,639
Yeah?

1287
01:24:59,711 --> 01:25:02,545
Happy birthday, Shinichi...

1288
01:25:04,112 --> 01:25:05,184
After all...

1289
01:25:06,184 --> 01:25:11,017
I... might never
get to say it again...

1290
01:25:11,804 --> 01:25:12,804
Ran...

1291
01:25:23,466 --> 01:25:29,242
♪ Arm in arm, a merry couple strolled by,
their voices just bursting out ♪

1292
01:25:29,266 --> 01:25:31,674
Cut it...

1293
01:25:31,698 --> 01:25:33,698
Cut whichever color you want...

1294
01:25:33,789 --> 01:25:37,090
But... what if I get it wrong?

1295
01:25:37,115 --> 01:25:38,817
It doesn't matter.

1296
01:25:38,842 --> 01:25:41,442
We're goners anyway,
once time is up...

1297
01:25:41,466 --> 01:25:44,366
So choose your color...

1298
01:25:44,983 --> 01:25:46,008
B-but...

1299
01:25:46,032 --> 01:25:49,065
♪ I grew a little jealous
as I was reminded that you weren't here ♪

1300
01:25:49,201 --> 01:25:52,727
Don't worry! I'll be right here with you
until you're done cutting!

1301
01:25:52,880 --> 01:25:55,408
Don't worry! I'll be right here with you
until you're done cutting!

1302
01:25:55,432 --> 01:25:57,256
♪ You know, when my heart
lets its guard down, it wants to be weak ♪

1303
01:25:57,281 --> 01:25:59,001
We'll be together when we die...

